      <profileDesc>
         <abstract>
            <p>The landlord (chaudhri)
               <persName ref="#purshottamDas">Purshottam Das</persName>
                is instructed to appear in <placeName ref="#ujjain">Ujjain</placeName> regarding the
               affairs of a district (pargana). The endorsement in the margin urges the proper
               management of that district. While undated, the document is from the lifetime of <persName ref="#purshottamDas">Purshottam Das</persName>.
            </p>
