   <text>
      <body>
         <pb n="1r" facs="lf_pDas_1660_dai_lns235ms_z_r.jpg"/>
         <div xml:id="orig_div1" xml:lang="ara" type="invocation" rend="top centre">
            <p>هو</p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="orig_div2" xml:lang="per" type="authorisation" rend="right margin">
            <p><stamp type="seal"><mentioned>
               <gap/>
               <unclear><persName ref="#aurangzebAlamgir">عالم گیر</persName></unclear>
               <gap/>
            </mentioned></stamp></p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="orig_div3" xml:lang="per" type="maintext">
            <p>
               <lb/>زبده الاقران
               <persName ref="#purshottamDas">پرسوتم داس</persName>
                چودهری پرگنه
               <placeName ref="#pgDhar">دهار</placeName>
               را انهاء آنکه
               <lb/>خطی که فرستاده بود بمُطالعه در آمد انچه از حقیقت پته
               <placeName ref="#sitapuri">سیتاپوری</placeName>
               <lb/>نوشته بود ظاهر شد
               عنقریب که اینجانب بدار الفتح
               <placeName ref="#ujjain">اوجین</placeName>
               <lb/>میرسد آن زبده الاقران در
               <placeName ref="#ujjain">اوجین</placeName>
               آمده حاضر شود
               <lb/>که چودریان و قانونگویان پرگنه
               <placeName ref="#lawani">لوانی</placeName>
                را نیز بحضور طلب داشته
               <lb/>بحقیقت طرفین وارسیده هرچه حق و نفس الامر خواهد بود
               <lb/>مقرر کرده خواهد شد
               <space/>
                زیاده چه نگاشته شود
               <g ref="#faqat">فقط</g>
            </p>
         </div>
         
         <div xml:id="orig_div4" xml:lang="per" type="authorisation" rend="right margin">
            <p>
               <lb/>مکرر آنکه چون پرگنه مذکور
               <lb/>بخالصه والا تعلق گرفته تا بر هر
               <lb/>طریقه راستی و درستی را پیش گرفته در لوازم
               <lb/>دولتخهاهی و نیکو خدمتی و افزونی کشتکار
               <unclear>چند قرار</unclear>
               <lb/>بکار برد
               <app>
                  <rdg cert="high">هر</rdg>
                  <rdg cert="low">که</rdg>
               </app>
                باعث محبات او درین است
               <g ref="#faqat">فقط</g>
            </p>
         </div>
         
         <pb n="1v" facs="lf_pDas_1660_dai_lns235ms_z_v.jpg"/>
         
         <div xml:id="orig_div5" xml:lang="per" type="laterAddition" rend="top centre">
            <p><foreign>نمبر</foreign>
               <num>۴۱</num>
            </p>
         </div>
         
         <div corresp="#orig_div1" xml:id="trans_div1">
            <p>He [God] is</p>
         </div>
         <div corresp="#orig_div2" xml:id="trans_div2">
            <p>
               <stamp type="seal">Round black ink seal<mentioned>
                  <gap/>
                  <unclear><persName ref="#aurangzebAlamgir">Alamgir</persName></unclear>
                  <gap/>
               </mentioned></stamp>
            </p>
         </div>
         <div corresp="#orig_div3" xml:id="trans_div3">
            <p><lb/>Eminent among Contemporaries
               <persName ref="#purshottamDas">Purshottam Das</persName>
               <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_chaudhri">chaudhri</ref> of <ref type="glossary"
                  target="#gl_pargana">pargana</ref>
               <placeName ref="#pgDhar">Dhar</placeName>
                is informed that
               <lb/>the letter that [you] had sent has come to our attention. That which you have
               written about the facts of the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_patta">patta</ref> of
               <placeName ref="#sitapuri">Sitapuri</placeName>
               <lb/>has become known.
               Shortly, when this party [the author] reaches the Abode of Victory
               <placeName ref="#ujjain">Ujjain</placeName>,
               <lb/>that Eminent among Contemporaries should come to
               <placeName ref="#ujjain">Ujjain</placeName> and present himself
               <lb/>[so] that, the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_chaudhri">chaudhris</ref> and <ref
                  type="glossary" target="#gl_qanungo">qanungos</ref> of <ref type="glossary"
                  target="#gl_pargana">pargana</ref>
               <placeName ref="#lawani">Lawani</placeName>
                also being summoned to the Lord,
               <lb/>[and] the facts of the two parties being obtained, whatever [matter] will be
               right and true
               <lb/>will be confirmed.
               <space/>
                What more shall be written?
               <g ref="#faqat">Nothing further.</g>
            </p>
         </div>
         <div corresp="#orig_div4" xml:id="trans_div4">
            <p><lb/>It is repeated that since the aforementioned <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_pargana"
                  >pargana</ref>
               <lb/>had been taken into the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_khalisa">khalisa</ref> so
               that in each
               <lb/>manner righteousness and correctness are exhibited, [and] for the necessary things of
               <lb/>loyalty towards the government and good service and the increase of agriculture,
               <unclear>several <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_qarar">qarars</ref></unclear>
               <lb/>shall be drawn up. <app><rdg cert="high">Every</rdg><rdg cert="low">For the</rdg></app> cause of his affection is in this.
               <g ref="#faqat">Nothing further.</g>
            </p>
         </div>
         <div corresp="#orig_div5" xml:id="trans_div5">
            <p>Number 41</p>
         </div>
      </body>
